<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{قَفَّيْنَا عَلَى آثَارِهِم}</span> ... أَتْبَعْنَاهُمْ، وَبَعَثْنَا بَعْدَهُمْ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{وَرَهْبَانِيَّةً}</span> ... غُلُوًّا فِي التَّعَبُّدِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{مَا كَتَبْنَاهَا}</span> ... مَا فَرَضْنَاهَا.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{ابْتِغَاءَ}</span> ... فَعَلُوهَا مِنْ عِنْدِ أَنْفُسِهِمْ يَطْلُبُونَ ...<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c2">(٢٧)</span> ... <span class="c3">{فَمَا رَعَوْهَا}</span> ... مَا قَامُوا بِهَا حَقَّ القِيَامِ، بَلْ بَدَّلُوا وَخَالَفُوا.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c2">(٢٨)</span> ... <span class="c3">{كِفْلَيْنِ}</span> ... ضِعْفَيْنِ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c2">(٢٩)</span> ... <span class="c3">{لِئَلَّا يَعْلَمَ}</span> ... أَعْطَاكُمُ اللهُ ذَلِكَ لِأَجْلِ أَنْ يَعْلَمَ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>